Passage of the Department of State Authorization Act, with the Public Diplomacy Modernization Act provisions, is a vital step to strengthening American foreign policy and ensuring our State Department workers are able to work efficiently and effectively. 

#ksleg #ks02
Inside this bill, is language from my bill, The Public Diplomacy Modernization Act, which takes great steps to evaluate the performance of our public outreach overseas and steward taxpayer dollars.

Today, for the first time since 2002, the House passed the Department of State Authorization Act. I am pleased my colleagues and I were able to work in a bipartisan way, to send a strong message to our diplomats that we have their back.
